Hi All,

Thanks for all you've done to change the signage and information about court bookings Martina.

Nicole, are you able to please provide Martina with support to change the information on the booking page? We are changing the booking availability due to COVID.

We also need to try to blank out Monday-Friday so this can't be booked by the public. Nicole do you know is there a way to make this hidden or do we need to book it out ourselves so it's not available?
